go to Lingzhou personally.

697
00:32:40,620 --> 00:32:41,880
Whether alive or dead,

698
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:43,200
I will bring Yu back.

699
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:44,860
You want to go to Lingzhou?

700
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:48,010
For the past few months,

701
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:50,480
I've been investigating
the Lizhou matter.

