[Qi'an Hall]

715
00:33:46,120 --> 00:33:48,480
Your Highness, the food is getting cold.

716
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:50,160
Why don't you start eating first?

717
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:51,280
Once Princess Consort returns,

718
00:33:51,280 --> 00:33:53,140
