00:42:04,120 --> 00:42:06,360
Also, Princess Consort's soft jade pillow

929
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:07,640
should be brought along as well.

930
00:42:07,640 --> 00:42:08,290
Yes.

931
00:42:09,520 --> 00:42:10,480
Tan. You’ve truly

